
microsoft-windows-devices-midi2 provides CMake target:

    find_package(microsoft-windows-devices-midi2 CONFIG REQUIRED)

It also sets the following:
    MIDI2_WINRT_WINMD to the full path to the Microsoft.Windows.Devices.Midi2.winmd file
    MIDI2_WINDOWS_SDK_VERSION to the version of the Windows SDK used to generate the projections
    MIDI2_HEADERS_ROOT_FOLDER to the root location of the necessary include files
    MIDI2_HEADERS_INIT_FOLDER for the initialization headers under the root header folder
    MIDI2_HEADERS_WINRT_FOLDER for the winrt projection headers under the root header folder
